------------------------------------------------------------

1. OVERVIEW
   This package contains every Stata *.do* script and support file
   needed to reproduce the results in:

     “Right-to-Work Laws, Union Decline, and Employer Power:
      Evidence from Staggered Reforms in U.S. Labor Markets.”

   • Downloads and cleans raw data
   • Builds analysis datasets
   • Regenerates all figures and tables

------------------------------------------------------------
2. FOLDER STRUCTURE

  Code/                  replication .do files
     |_Archive/          older code
     | Logs/             Stata logs
  Data/                  raw data  (empty – git-ignored)
     | CPS_ORG_Data/
     | CPS_ORG_dta/
  Intm/                  processed data
  Presentations/
     |_Archive/          previous versions
     | Bibliography/
     | Figures/
     | Formatting/
     | Sections/
     | Tables/
  LICENSE.txt
  README.txt  (this file)
  README.md   Markdown version

------------------------------------------------------------
3. PREREQUISITES

  • Stata/SE or MP 18   (17/16 likely OK)
  • R 4.2+ with tidyverse (optional plots)
  • GNU Make  — or run .do files manually

------------------------------------------------------------
4. QUICK START   (demo mode)

  git clone https://github.com/al0-h/rtw_union_power.git
  cd rtw_union_power
  make demo      # builds a 100-row sample & runs toy DiD
  make clean     # removes temp files

(Full CPS pipeline requires IPUMS extracts; see Section 5.)

------------------------------------------------------------
5. STEP-BY-STEP REPLICATION GUIDE

  1. Copy RTW_Years.xlsx to Data/
  2. In Stata:  do Code/00_Master.do
     – Imports CPS, merges RTW dates, writes Intm/state_month_panel.dta
  3. do 03b_TWFE_HetT10.do   → TWFE estimates
  4. do 03c_CSDID_HetT10.do  → event-study plot
  5. Logs saved to Code/Logs/

------------------------------------------------------------
6. EXPECTED OUTPUT

  Script                Output                                Saved to
  --------------------  ------------------------------------  -------------------------------
  03b_TWFE_HetT10.do    TWFE estimates (high-union industries) Presentations/Tables/TWFE_HetT10.pdf
  03c_CSDID_HetT10.do   CSDID ATT event study                 Presentations/Figures/CSDID_HetT10.pdf

------------------------------------------------------------
7. TROUBLESHOOTING

  • “file RTW_Years.xlsx not found”  → place file in Data/
  • csdid missing  →  in Stata:  ssc install csdid
  • r(601) memory error  →  run Stata/MP or split years (see 01b script)

